snippet.title: Mayawati Attacks Modi Govt over Ban on Rs 500, 1000 Currency Notes

localized.description:
BSP supremo Mayawati attacks Prime Minister Narendra Modi government over ban on Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes. Mayawati said that PM Modi's Ghazipur's rally was failed.
